(72, 1, '2014-03-24 21:30:42', '2014-03-24 21:30:42', '<em>Looper</em>is a film that is, apparently, rather good. It even has that guy from<em>Inception</em>and<em>The Dark Knight Rises</em>in it.\r\n\r\nDepending on<strong>a community vote</strong>cast on the day of the meet, we may go to the 7:45pm viewing of<em>Looper</em>at the Showcase Cinema De Lux in Cabot Circus.\r\n\r\nTickets cost around 8.50. The performance is about two hours long, and with the inclusion of advertisements we shouldn''t expect to leave the cinema until after 10pm. Please take this into account when making your travel plans.', 'Looper, maybe?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'looper-maybe', '', '', '2014-03-24 21:30:42', '2014-03-24 21:30:42', '', 0, 'http://bristolbronies.dev/?post_type=meet&#038;p=72', 0, 'meet', '', 0),
(73, 1, '2014-03-24 21:32:23', '2014-03-24 21:32:23', 'The next meet is located on the<strong>13th of October, 2012</strong>.\r\n\r\nThis date has been chosen due to a fair spacing from the previous meet (22nd September) whilst also being a good time away from MCM at the end of the month, which I know a lot of people are attending. It is also in close proximity to October 10th, the<em>two year anniversary of My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic</em>.\r\n\r\nThere is little in the way of plans, and this will probably end up being another<abbr title="Bronies Aimlessly Bumble Around Bristol">BABAB</abbr>-styled meet, however we will <em>definitely</em>be paying a visit to Forbidden Planet (they''re now stocking wave five blind bags, also I told the staff we would be there).\r\n\r\nOther than that, we''re open to suggestions!', 'My Little Pony: Friendship is Two Years Old', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'my-little-pony-friendship-is-two-years-old', '', '', '2014-03-24 21:32:23', '2014-03-24 21:32:23', '', 0, 'http://bristolbronies.dev/?post_type=meet&#038;p=73', 0, 'meet', '', 0),
