(85, 1, '2014-03-24 22:12:45', '2014-03-24 22:12:45', '<em>My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic</em>#1 will have been out for a whole two days by now, so we''re assuming Forbidden Planet formation delta and heading up to our favourite geeky goods store to collect our pre-orders and probably splurge out on yet more blind bags. Followed, of course, by spending excessive amounts of time in Subway.', 'A Comical Adventure', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'a-comical-adventure', '', '', '2014-03-24 22:12:45', '2014-03-24 22:12:45', '', 0, 'http://bristolbronies.dev/?post_type=meet&#038;p=85', 0, 'meet', '', 0),
