(93, 1, '2014-03-24 22:39:57', '2014-03-24 22:39:57', 'We have no episode, no venue and no events. Screw it, we''re doing it old school!\r\n\r\nUnlike our last few meets, this one isn''t abiding by any schedule, we''re still meeting at Starbucks, but from midday onwards what we''re doing will be totally wild, wacky and made up on the fly.\r\n\r\nShall we say hello to our friendly neighbourhood Perfect Pizza Company? Shall we fawn over technology that none of us can really afford at Apple and PC World? Raid toy shops or pick up ponies at Forbidden Planet? (Well, that last one is pretty likely.) It''s all down to<em>you</em>!', 'The Utterly Unplanned Mid-Hiatus Pony Meet', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-mid-hiatus-pony-meet', '', '', '2014-03-24 22:39:57', '2014-03-24 22:39:57', '', 0, 'http://bristolbronies.dev/?post_type=meet&#038;p=93', 0, 'meet', '', 0),
