(119, 1, '2014-03-25 09:16:03', '2014-03-25 09:16:03', '<p>Fillies and Gentlecolts, you are cordially invited to attend The Grand Galloping Cosplay Meet. Organised by Bristol Bronies in cooperation with Equestria in the South West of England.</p>\r\n<div class="gg-intro">Fillies and Gentlecolts, you are cordially invited to attend <h1>The Grand Galloping Cosplay Meet</h1></div>\r\n<p><em>Organised by</em>\r\n<a href="http://bristolbronies.co.uk">Bristol Bronies</a> in cooperation with <a href="http://www.facebook.com/groups/148326595278598/">Equestria in the South West of England</a></p>\r\n<p>A day of organised <strong>fun</strong> and <strong>frivolity</strong>\r\nto be had by those donning the <em>queerest</em> of costumes;\r\nwith a <strong>grand prize</strong> for that which is deemed the queerest!</p>\r\n<p>All costumes welcomed, with equestrian preferred.</p>\r\n<p><em>To commence at</em>\r\neleven o''clock, on the morning of\r\nSaturday, the twenty-ninth of June,\r\ntwo thousand and thirteen, sharp</p>', 'The Grand Galloping Cosplay Meet', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-grand-galloping-meet', '', '', '2014-03-25 12:04:38', '2014-03-25 12:04:38', '', 0, 'http://bristolbronies.dev/?post_type=meet&#038;p=119', 0, 'meet', '', 0),
