(129, 1, '2014-03-25 09:40:15', '2014-03-25 09:40:15', '<em>Equestria Girls</em> is showing in Bristol on 10th August. How about we check it out? \r\n\r\nWe''ll be seeing the showing at the Showcase Cinema de Lux in Cabot Circus at 1pm. We plan to meet up ahead of time so that people can buy tickets and food if they need to, and probably hanging out for a couple of hours afterwards. \r\n\r\nTo save yourself time (and potentially money), as well as to make sure you land a seat, we recommend that you buy your ticket online <a href="http://www.showcasecinemas.co.uk/films/my-little-pony-equestria-girls">at the Showcase Cinemas website</a> (make sure that you select "Bristol Cinema de Lux" from the dropdown!)', 'Equestria Girls', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'equestria-girls', '', '', '2014-03-25 09:40:58', '2014-03-25 09:40:58', '', 0, 'http://bristolbronies.dev/?post_type=meet&#038;p=129', 0, 'meet', '', 0),
