(152, 1, '2014-03-25 10:02:03', '2014-03-25 10:02:03', 'The season 4 premiere meet!\r\n\r\nWe''re limited on space, so please RSVP for this meet using the form on the right in order to guarantee your place!\r\n\r\n<h2>Meet plan</h2>\r\n\r\n<strong>1100&ndash;1200 Starbucks</strong>\r\nDrink coffee! Turn up on time! It''s what all the cool kids are doing!\r\n\r\n<strong>1200&ndash;1330 The Knight''s Templar</strong>\r\nFood! Drink! Bricks! \r\n\r\n<strong>1330&ndash;1630 Hydra Books</strong>\r\nWe''re back in the bookshop! Let''s do things!\r\n\r\n<em>Episode viewing: ???</em>\r\nWe know absolutely nothing about the episode yet! And with promises made about it relating to Twilight''s recent transformation, what mystery''s will it reveal?\r\n\r\n<em>Lauren Faust and Company''s Amazing Ponydrome</em>\r\nYet more pony video cinema to watch randomly.\r\n\r\n<em>Card Games Against Pony-anity</em>\r\nCard games in bookshops! Featuring <em>Cards Against Humanity</em>, <em>Flame War</em>, and more!\r\n\r\n<strong>1630&ndash;1730 Bristol wanderin''</strong>\r\nA little bit of wandering around town. Pop into some shops, grab a little bit to eat. \r\n\r\nThis meet is shorter than most of our monthly events, and we have not allocated time to visit some of our regular locations. Attendees are of course free to make their own arrangements to trudge on up to Forbidden Planet!', 'Twilight Sparkle''s New Groove', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'twilight-sparkles-new-groove', '', '', '2014-03-25 10:02:03', '2014-03-25 10:02:03', '', 0, 'http://bristolbronies.dev/?post_type=meet&#038;p=152', 0, 'meet', '', 0),
