(183, 1, '2013-07-08 10:57:16', '2013-07-08 10:57:16', 'For meets as mobile as ours, the weather conditions on the day of any event is actually something pretty important. Will you need a warm jacket, an umbrella, or a suit of chainmail? Are you likely to be bogged down by snow or slowed down by heat? These are all important questions. \r\n\r\nTo this effect, we now introduce a little snippet we call "Forecast" to the pages of all upcoming meets, giving you a quick overview of that day''s expected weather conditions in the predominantly-sunny-with-some-cloud city of Bristol!\r\n\r\n<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/weather-beta.png" alt="weather-beta" width="880" height="436" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-186" />', '[Beta] Forecast', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'beta-forecast', '', '', '2014-03-25 12:08:35', '2014-03-25 12:08:35', '', 0, 'http://bristolbronies.dev/?post_type=news&#038;p=183', 0, 'news', '', 0),
