(198, 1, '2014-03-29 07:44:57', '2014-03-29 07:44:57', 'Another year, another TableTop Day. We''ll once again be joining the folks at Forbidden Planet to try out a range of modern tabletop gaming classics including Carcassonne, Ticket to Ride Europe, and Star Wars X-Wing. (I can personally recommend Ticket to Ride as an awesome game.)\r\n\r\nThis will be followed by casual hanging out and, most likely, subway sandwiches; so drop on down won''tcha? \r\n\r\n<small>Header photograph by <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/ifreak77">Francesco Marino</a>. Used under Creative Commons.</small>', 'The Games Bronies Play', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-games-bronies-play', '', '', '2014-03-29 08:01:15', '2014-03-29 08:01:15', '', 0, 'http://bristolbronies.dev/?post_type=meet&#038;p=198', 0, 'meet', '', 0),
